$interpreted:
Puggi: Whew~ Finally made it to Whistlewood Valley.
But my this place is huge. Where am I suppose to find Pang?
Puggi: Seems like it's time for my sharp instincts to take action again.

Puggi: Hmph, don't even need to think.
Ain't it obvious which way I'm going?
Puggi: This footprint that looks like it's from a beast, I'm willing to bet it's from chubby fatso Pang! We'll certainly find him by following these footprints!

Puggi: W, what in Puggi's name is this behemoth...
Hmm, isn't that?

Puggi: W, what should I do...
Nobody's going to come and help this time...
Puggi: Screw it, who cares no help is coming! For the sake of my best buddy, I will show you no mercy!!!

Puggi: The heck, so you're not Pang after all.
You just have a tail that looks similar to his!
Puggi: Hmm, so I assume that this footprint is yours as well?
Puggi: Now that I observe it closely... this print is too small even for baby Pang.

Puggi: Whew~ So it was just a false alarm~
Well, since we got that out of the way, time to resume the search...
Puggi: Hey, why is it so dark? Did someone turn off the lights? Hello~ anybody here...

Puggi: Hmm? What's this?
A backpack?
Puggi: Oooohhh, lots of treasure! JACKPOT!
